  <brief_title>Elidel-Study: Elidel in Patients With Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Control of Therapy With Elidel vs Placebo in Patients With Atopic Dermatitis Using Bioengineering Methods</official_title>
  <sponsors>
