  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Atopic dermatitis is a common disease. Emollients and Elidel have both shown to be effective
      to treat this disease. The research question is, whether the effective component (Elidel) is
      better than the emollient to improve the skin function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
